        .content.content-2
          h3 Our Custom Boxes
          p Custom boxes are the backbone of our business. Regardless of what you need to box, our team will work closely with you to ensure all of your packaging needs are met. 
          p We are able to offer:
          ul
            li Custom box sizes, shapes and cuts
            li Custom foam inserts 
            li Custom colour printing
          button.cta Learn More About Custom Boxes
        
        .content.content-3 
          h3 How to measure a box
          .figure 
            img(src="./assets/images/measure-box.png", alt="how to measure a box")
          ol 
            li Measure the length of the box first. This is the long side of the box on the side of the longest flap.
            li Next, turn the box 90 degrees and measure the width, which is the side with the shorter flap.
            li Last, measure the height of the package. This will be measured with the flaps closed, from top to bottom.
        
        .content.content-4 
          h3 Our Shipping Areas
          p We offer fast shipping services to locations across Southwestern Ontario, including Windsor, Sarnia, London, Woodstock, Kitchener-Waterloo, Cambridge, Guelph, Hamilton, and the Greater Toronto Area (GTA). 
          p Additionally, we provide domestic and  international shipping to nearly any destination worldwide.
